8]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00823">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 18. 7. 1898</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
